 177	
 178	## Application Status Flow
 179	
 180	1. **EN_ATTENTE** (Pending) - Initial status when application is submitted
 181	2. **ACCEPTED** - Application approved by admin
 182	3. **REJECTED** - Application rejected by admin with reason
 183	
 184	## File Upload
 185	
 186	- Supports PDF files only
 187	- Files are stored in the `uploads/` directory
 188	- Each child can have one PDF document
 189	- File names are automatically generated to prevent conflicts
